{"tid":2133252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭錦滿被DQ原因之一：於2016年表明繼續支持港獨，確認書針對港獨主張候選人","createTime":"2020-07-31T03:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T09:11:53.000Z","uid":5843,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b24f0da28b8bfc26d8e699b98d00cc43ce3493ff","tid":2133252,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:12:07.000Z","msg":"【表明繼續支持港獨　鄭錦滿：確認書針對港獨主張候選人】<br />\n<br />\n已報名參選今屆立法會港島直選的熱血公民成員鄭錦滿，今早（7月25日）接受商台節目訪問時，再次重申在簽署選管會新增的確認書後，將堅持政治立場，繼續支持港獨。<br />\n<br />\n港島區立法會直選參選人、熱血公民成員鄭錦滿今早連同幾名年輕候選人，包括民族黨陳浩天、本土民主前線梁天琦和青年新政黃俊傑，齊齊接受商業電台節目「在晴朗的一天出發」訪問，回應選管會新增確認書的事件，被問到立場如何時，鄭回應自己將「堅持政治立場」、「繼續支持港獨」，更指以後的訪問、選舉論壇都會繼續堅持有關政治立場。<br />\n<br />\n鄭錦滿又指，提名報名表中已有「我擁護基本法及效忠香港特別行政區」，選管會特意抽基本法中的三條出來，只是「玩嘢」、「針對有港獨主張的候選人」。<br />\n<br />\n港島已報名名單如下：<br />\n鄭錦滿名單、許智峯名單、葉劉淑儀名單、郭偉强名單、張國鈞名單、羅冠聰名單、司馬文名單、王維基名單、陳淑莊名單<br />\n<br />\n新東已報名名單如下：<br />\n林卓廷名單、容海恩名單、梁天琦名單、方國珊名單、李梓敬名單、葛珮帆名單、張超雄名單、范國威名單、陳克勤名單、侯志強名單、鄧家彪名單、楊岳橋名單、梁國雄名單、陳志全名單<br />\n<br />\n新西已報名名單如下：<br />\n陳恒鑌名單、何君堯名單、黃俊傑名單、陳浩天名單、馮檢基名單、周永勤名單、田北辰名單、梁志祥名單、黃潤達名單、朱凱廸名單、郭家麒名單、麥美娟名單、尹兆堅名單、黃浩銘名單<br />\n<br />\n#港獨 #立法會選舉<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-25-2016/31803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-25-2016%2F31803&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG13vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=1854f3b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-25-2016/31803</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mp13B6K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMp13B6K.png&h=e903a0e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近fb post: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/800421050019891/posts/3242385675823404/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F800421050019891%2Fposts%2F3242385675823404%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG13vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=b347c452\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/800421050019891/posts/3242385675823404/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"bc8d20222bbe154371acaf9e5fbe4dd3ab1f4686","tid":2133252,"uid":341316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e3cfbc62e691451ea94aaa4fcc09921db745d8","tid":2133252,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />派蝗上去選實冇事<br />\n永瀆國安法"},{"pid":"b2cfde6d281c60696d903dec7e6fd40bd14e2284","tid":2133252,"uid":7484,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:16:31.000Z","msg":"熱共狗，拉"},{"pid":"e51aeea27a390cbc4b2b7b0355a7007c69e32cf3","tid":2133252,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60af35e47707ada4701a1d472d7fe876a25dc6b2","tid":2133252,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:36:12.000Z","msg":"佢俾人dq左法子頂唔頂得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼食泥"},{"pid":"648564b90fc66ec24b59b0a013af3ccd1e4da3a2","tid":2133252,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:01:11.000Z","msg":"唔俾2017-20改變睇法？"},{"pid":"8247a28f72816bf6ef455d358b746d5b6c8db7f1","tid":2133252,"uid":297241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a678f5007f0a9854d21392b89dfc8f5beb2beb0","tid":2133252,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8247a28f72816bf6ef455d358b746d5b6c8db7f1","tid":2133252,"uid":297241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /